aspect_dynamics.v1.json — Schema + Semantics
1. Purpose of this file
Defines, in code:
What each major aspect does as a system interaction
Constructive vs distorted expressions (non-moralized)
Allowed language patterns
Forbidden language patterns (benefic/malefic, alarmist)
Intensity modifiers (orb, activation) framed as salience, not consequence
Used by:
Interpretation bundle creation
Interpreter (Layer 2)
QA enforcement
Repetition control (metaphor rotation)
No aspect meaning is allowed unless it exists here.

